ur feedback in balancing them further before we send them live.'<br><br>The most controversial changes include:<br><br>Mana Burn (Wiz) and Life Burn (Nec) now cap at 10,000 damage. <br>Mana Burn (Wiz) and Life Burn (Nec) can no longer deal a critical blast. <br>Dire Charmed (Enc, Dru, Nec) pets can no longer be buffed. <br>Dire Charmed (Enc, Dru, Nec) pets will now only deal 66% of their normal damage. <br>Dire Charm Spells will now have a small chance to be resisted. <br>Healing Gift will now use up double mana when a critical heal succesfully lands. <br>For a full list of the complete changes be sure to read the full announcement. <br><br>Click here for details. <br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/viewarticle.asp?Article=4205">eq.castersrealm.com/viewarticle.asp?Article=4205</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <p>--<a href=http://www.clubfu.com/view_player.php?uid=82>Castiran</a><br>60 Crusader - Club Fu, Bristlebane<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubelzebuth666.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Belzebuth666</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ironworksforum.com/ubb/noncgi/smiles/double0smile.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 238<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/1/02 10:31:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15123.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.ironworksforum.com/ubb/noncgi/smiles/double0smile.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ALT ADVANCEMENT = nerfed on test ! :(</span><hr size=1> look at a calendar... <p>Belze L`Valeureux Crusader of the 6000th lfg <BR>_______________VISION_______________            </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title